{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Summary</h2><br>David is a game. A game about physics and enemies. A game about struggles and life. A game about David.<br><br>This game is designed to be difficult. I poured myself into developing this game for nights and nights and nights. It's almost tough to share. I hope it feels strangely personal.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Description</h2>You play David, an awfully small abstracted chosen hero tossed into a blissfully simple world overrun by giant culminations of evil physics-beasts. As David, you are given a slingshot-esque gift that you will have to use to conquer your colossus foes. Hold, aim, and fling to attack (Angry Birds\u2122 style!).<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2>a 9-level Campaign, 3 Additional Levels, a Survival/Arena/RPG mode, a Secret Basket-ball-pit Minigame, and hats!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Soundtrack</h2>A six song EP soundtrack is included with purchase &quot;...that feels like FEZ and is similarly wonderful!&quot; - Laser Dog<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346180/extras/davidonsteam-02-widesm2.png?t=1734013900\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Greed on Very.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/346180/80a30e1f126160902b61a8290a2f2d10f1f15e3a.jpg"},{"name":"Anger on Very","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/346180/80a30e1f126160902b61a8290a2f2d10f1f15e3a.jpg"},{"name":"Wolf on Very.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/346180/80a30e1f126160902b61a8290a2f2d10f1f15e3a.jpg"},{"name":"Anxt on Very.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/346180/80a30e1f126160902b61a8290a2f2d10f1f15e3a.jpg"},{"name":"Lies on Very.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/346180/80a30e1f126160902b61a8290a2f2d10f1f15e3a.jpg"},{"name":"Brood on Very.","